Package: BRVM
Type: Package
Title: PAckage to retrieve historical data of companies listed on Brvm Stock Exchange 
Version: 1.3.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("SESSIE","Koffi Frederic", email = "koffisessie@gmail.com", role = c("aut","cre","cph")),
    person("Abdoul","Oudouss Diakité", email = "spsanderson@gmail.com", role = "aut"),
    person("Steven","Sanderson", email = "spsanderson@gmail.com", role = "aut"))
Description: BRVM is an R package that provides real-time data from the BRVM (“Regional Securities Exchange SA” call Bourse Régionale des Valeurs Mobilières in french). As a goal, we want to facilitate access to data for all users of the R programming language. This package includes a variety of data accessible just by function call.
